===Noun===
'''toot'''
#The noise of a [[horn]] or [[whistle]].
#:''He gave a little '''toot''' of the horn, to get their attention.''

===Verb===

'''to toot'''

#To [[stand out]], or be [[prominent]].
#To [[peep]]; to look [[narrowly]].
#To [[see]]; to [[spy]].
#To [[flatulate]].
#To make the noise of a horn or whistle.

